para_trans: Administrative approval for the foreign visit of Hon'ble Minister (Information Technology) and Hon'ble Principal Secretary (Information Technology) to participate in the IoT Solution World Congress and Barcelona Cyber Security Congress 2025, and sanction of the related expenditure.
Reference:- Government Resolution No. VDR-1025/C.R.73/IT, dated 25th April, 2025.

Fira Barcelona has invited the Government of Maharashtra to participate in the "IoT Solution World Congress and Barcelona Cyber Security Congress 2025" scheduled from 15 to 18 "May 2025 (including travel period) in Barcelona, Spain. The Hon'ble Chief Minister approved the participation of the Hon'ble Minister (Information Technology) and the Hon'ble Principal Secretary (Information Technology) in this event. According to, administrative approval for the foreign tour to Barcelona was granted vide Government Resolution dated 25 April 2025.

Administrative approval is hereby accredited for the participation of the Hon'ble Minister (Information Technology), the Hon'ble Principal Secretary (Information Technology), and the official delegation in the "IoT Solution World Congress and Barcelona Cyber Security Congress 2025" to be held from 13 "to 15" May 2025 at Barcelona, Spain.
